title: Australian diary. No. 133
brief_description: Magazine items: Heron sailing, Canberra. A poetic glimpse of Heron class yachts on Lake Burley Griffin; Pre-school kindergarten. A day at a kindergarten at which many children obviously enjoy facilities available under the supervision of trained staff; Modern dance. At the Fort Street Girls’ High School in Sydney, Modern dance is part of the physical education programme and many students enjoy these sessions. No other credits available.
